Class DockableSelectionSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • saf.core.ui.event.DockableSelectionSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    bibliothek.gui.dock.common.event.CFocusListener

    public class DockableSelectionSupport
extends java.lang.Object
implements bibliothek.gui.dock.common.event.CFocusListener
    Utility support class for managing dockable frame selection events. For this to be effective it must be added as CFocusListener to a CControl.
    Author:
    Nick Collier
